dictionary.description: A young man who probably knows much more than the elders who surround him on a daily basis. Regarded as a genius and a prodigy, Noel began working as head of the Survey Office of Akras Summoners' Hall at the tender age of 13. His main responsibilities include gathering data from the different worlds accessible via his surveys, and researching the Summoner Arts in order to gain a deeper understanding of them. He has made a lot of interesting discoveries through his endeavors, including very powerful Spheres, but he is perhaps best known for the various array of Mock Units he created to test the Legendary Summoner. As his knowledge grows with age, now he creates even more powerful and efficient models that once won fairly through his notoriously challenging trials, which can prove invaluable in battle.
